 "html": "<p>Vanaand is bitter koud in Hopefield.  Ek het &#8216;n gevoelte gekry om iets te maak wat koester.  Sjokolade is vreeslik vergewinsgesind. &#8211; selfs vir koue.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>8 croissants</li>\n<li>1 potjie nutella sjokoladesmeer</li>\n<li>500 ml room</li>\n<li>250 ml melk</li>\n<li>4 eiers</li>\n<li>5 ml vanillageursel</li>\n<li>125 ml strooisuiker</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-002.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-372\" alt=\"broodpoeding blog 002\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-002-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>sny die croissants middeldeur en smeer dit dik met die nutella<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-010.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-373\" alt=\"broodpoeding blog 010\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-010-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>Pak die gesmeerde croissants soos dakteels oor mekaar in &#8216;n oondvastebak.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-012.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-374\" alt=\"broodpoeding blog 012\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-012-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>Meng die room, melk, eiers, vanillageursel en strooisuiker goed.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-016.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-375\" alt=\"broodpoeding blog 016\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-016-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>Gooi dit oor die croissants. Laat dit staan vir 60 minute.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-018.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-376\" alt=\"broodpoeding blog 018\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-018-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>Bak dit vir 40 minute by 180 grade Celsius.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-022.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-377\" alt=\"broodpoeding blog 022\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-022-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>Haal dit uit die oond en eet dit met vla of roomys.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-036.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-378\" alt=\"broodpoeding blog 036\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/broodpoeding-blog-036-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
